@startuml A3_01_component_neo4j_graph_simple
title Neo4j Knowledge Graph – Simplified View

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #000000
  BorderThickness 1
}

rectangle "Neo4j Knowledge Graph" as NEO4J {
  rectangle "Entity Types\n(courses, majors, sections, students)" as ENTITIES
  rectangle "Relationships\n(prerequisites, requirements, equivalencies)" as RELATIONS
  rectangle "Graph Operations\n(traversal, path finding, queries)" as OPS
}

cloud "RAG Service" as RAG
cloud "Agent Service" as AGENT
cloud "Enrollment Service" as ENROLLMENT

RAG --> ENTITIES : entity extraction
RAG --> RELATIONS : relationship extraction
AGENT --> OPS : enrollment queries
ENROLLMENT --> OPS : prerequisites, requirements

note right of NEO4J
**Key Capabilities:**
- Prerequisites graph (course → course)
- Requirements graph (course → major/minor)
- Transfer equivalency mappings
- Course relationships (conflicts, co-requisites)
end note

@enduml

